  "title": "Principal Consultant",
  "description": "<p>• Manage and Lead end-to-end QA strategy across complex banking platforms (Temenos T24, Murex) covering SIT, UAT, regression, and integration testing.</p><p>• Own Control-M workload automation: batch job scheduling, dependency management, SLA monitoring, and failure recovery across multi-env landscapes.</p><p>• Design and execute automation frameworks using Selenium/UFT/QTP integrated with CI/CD pipelines (Jenkins, Maven).</p><p>• Validate document management workflows (OCR, indexing, metadata, retention) ensuring regulatory, risk, and audit compliance.</p><p>• Drive test governance, defect lifecycle management, and release readiness in agile, multi-vendor global programs.</p><p>• Collaborate with business, DevOps, infra, and data teams to ensure quality alignment with enterprise banking standards.</p>",
